文字部分在商品主体上/文字部分在商品主体上_0093.jpg.mt:
The beloved fragrant jeans that everyone likes have been made.
This pair is from the Chanel* spring/summer collection, so it's naturally on the thinner side.
But this pair is currently the most comfortable material among all the branded jeans I own—it's especially soft and cozy.
Every time I wear it privately and take photos, netizens always ask about this pair.
I didn’t want to switch to a very thick denim for autumn and winter, as it would lose the original feel.
So, I made two versions: one with the original thickness and a fleece-lined version.
The fleece-lined version isn’t as soft, but the cut is just as stylish.
I also added a black-gray color—I like to make more color options for good pants.
WUUUS 2024 F/W
src: 大家喜欢的香香牛仔裤做出来了 这条是chane*春夏款所以本身偏薄 但这条是目前我所有品牌牛仔裤里最好穿的材质特别舒服特别软 私下每次穿拍了照都会有网友问这条 我不想为了秋冬去换成很厚的牛仔布就失去了原版的味道 所以就做了两个版本 一个原版厚度一个加绒版  加绒版就没那么软了哈但裤型都是一样好看的 还加了一个黑灰色好穿的裤子就喜欢做多点颜色
